data.description: Welcome home to this wonderful bi-level home in the beautiful, mature Charleswood 6th Development! You will love the spacious open concept letting in tons of natural light, vaulted ceilings, and eat up island. The primary bedroom on the upper floor is massive and features an ensuite bath and walk-in closet. Downstairs you will find a large family room with built ins, two additional bedrooms, a bathroom, as well as laundry/utility. Enjoy your massive two tier deck overlooking your fully fenced yard. You won't want to miss this one, so call today to set up a showing!
